conformanceStatements.description: MSH-1 (Field Separator) SHALL be literal '|' (ASCII 124).
MSH-2 (Encoding Characters) SHALL be literal value '^~\&' (ASCII 94, 126, 92, and 38 respectively).
MSH-7.1 (Date/Time of Message.Time) SHALL be expressed with a minimum precision of the nearest minute and be represented in the following format: 'YYYYMMDDHHMM[SS[.S[S[S[S]]]]] [+/-ZZZZ]'
MSH-11.1 (Processing ID.Processing ID) SHALL have a value in the set of literal values: "P" for Production, "D" for Debug or "T" for Training.
MSH-12.1 (Version ID.Version ID) SHALL have a value '2.5.1'
MSH-9 (Message Type) SHALL be the literal value: 'ADT^A01^ADT_A01' for Admission Messages
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
						<FORALL>
							<!-- First check that all values are present because PlainText returns true when something is not present -->
							<Presence Path="9[1].1[1]"/>
							<Presence Path="9[1].2[1]"/>
							<Presence Path="9[1].3[1]"/>
							<!-- now check the values -->
							<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="9[1].1[1]" Text="ADT"/>
							<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="9[1].2[1]" Text="A01"/>
							<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="9[1].3[1]" Text="ADT_A01"/>
						</FORALL>
					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: MSH-15 (Accept Acknowledgment Type) SHALL be the literal value: 'AL'.

children.name: Software Certified Version or Release Number

conformanceStatements.description: EVN-2.1 (Recorded Date/Time of Message.Time) SHALL be expressed with a minimum precision of the nearest minute, and be represented in the following format: 'YYYYMMDDHHMM[SS[.S[S[S[S]]]]] [+/- ZZZZ]'
PID-1 (Set ID - PID) SHALL be valued with the constant value '1'.
PID-5 (Patient Name) SHALL be valued as |~^^^^^^S| or |~^^^^^^U|).
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
						<FORALL>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].1[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].2[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].3[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].4[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].5[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<NOT>
								<Presence Path="5[2].6[1]"/>
							</NOT>
							<Presence Path="5[2].7[1]"/>
							<StringList CSV="S,U" Path="5[2].7[1]"/>
						</FORALL>
					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: OBX-1(SetID) for the first instance of an OBX Segment SHALL have the Literal Value of '1'. Each following occurrence SHALL be numbered consecutively.
If OBX 3.1 (Observation Identifier) is valued with 21612-7 AGE-REPORTED (LOINC), then OBX-6.1 (Unit Identifier) SHALL be valued to a member of the set: PHVS_AgeUnit_SyndromicSurveillance
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
						<IMPLY>
							<AND>
								<Presence Path="3[1].1[1]"/>
								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].1[1]" Text="21612-7"/>
							</AND>
							<ValueSet BindingLocation="1" BindingStrength="R" Path="6[1]" ValueSetID="PHVS_AgeUnit_SyndromicSurveillance"/>
						</IMPLY>
					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: If OBX 3.1 (Observation Identifier) is valued with 11289-6 BODY TEMPERATURE, INITIAL (LOINC), then OBX-6.1 (Unit Identifier) SHALL be valued to a member of the set: PHVS_TemperatureUnit_UCUM
conformanceStatements.assertion:
<Assertion xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
						<IMPLY>
							<AND>
								<Presence Path="3[1].1[1]"/>
								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].1[1]" Text="11289-6"/>
							</AND>
							<ValueSet BindingLocation="1" BindingStrength="R" Path="6[1]" ValueSetID="PHVS_TemperatureUnit_UCUM"/>
						</IMPLY>
					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: If OBX 3.1 (Observation Identifier) is valued with 59408-5 OXYGEN SATURATION IN ARTERIAL BLOOD BY PULSE OXIMETRY (LOINC),, then OBX-6.1 (Unit Identifier) SHALL be valued to a member of the set: PHVS_TemperatureUnit_UCUM.

							</AND>

conformanceStatements.description: If OBX 3.1 (Observation Identifier) is valued with 8661-1 CHIEF COMPLAINT-REPORTED (LOINC), then OBX-2 (Value Type) SHALL be valued 'TX'.
conformanceStatements.assertion:

						<IMPLY>
							<FORALL>
								<Presence Path="3[1].1[1]"/>
								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].1[1]" Text="8661-1"/>
								<Presence Path="3[1].3[1]"/>
								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].3[1]" Text="LN"/>
							</FORALL>
							<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="2[1]" Text="TX"/>
						</IMPLY>
					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: If OBX 3.1 (Observation Identifier) is valued with SS002 TREATING FACILITY LOCATION (PHINQUESTION), then OBX-2 (Value Type) SHALL be valued 'XAD'.

								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].1[1]" Text="SS002"/>

								<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="3[1].3[1]" Text="PHINQUESTION"/>

							<PlainText IgnoreCase="false" Path="2[1]" Text="XAD"/>

					</Assertion>

conformanceStatements.description: DG1-1 (Set ID) for the first occurrence of a DG1 Segment SHALL have the Literal Value of '1'.  Each following occurrence SHALL be numbered consecutively
DG1-3.3 SHALL be valued "I9CDX" or "I10C" or "SCT".
DG1-6 Diagnosis Type SHALL be either A (Admitting), F (Final) or W (Working).
